commit.message:
upgrade to java 11 (#969)

bump dependency versions

change dependency versions

add lombok config as default behavoir has now changed

bump io.netty and spring-cloud-contract-wiremock, set source compatibility, test remove spring proxy autoconfig

move print statement to doFirst() to avoid feeding its stdout as argument to another task

fix tests

bump flyway

log additional flyway info

Refactor HealthCheckTest to wait for mocks to be ready

remove old migration call

remove unnecessary throws error for function

align dependency versions

remove debug logging flywayNoOpStrategy class

align serenity versions

update documentation
fix ambiguous delegation error

apply fix from FR for fixing flakey tests with idam failing to return token

see for reference: https://github.com/hmcts/finrem-case-orchestration-service/pull/437

removed unused logger

fix CVE's

increase retry count

add proxy config
